name: WTB ThickSlick Comp Tire
description: This 700c x 25mm tire employs a burly casing designed to withstand the roughest urban conditions, while the no-nonsense, slick design provides the bite you need in the concrete jungle.

name: WTB All Terrain Tire
description: 26in x 1.95in all terrain tire is comfortable enough to take on a touring adventure and stable enough to take off-road

name: Bontrager T1 Road Tire
description: Ideal for touring, training or recreational riding, this 27in x 1-1/4in road tire feature a super tough nylon casing and durable compound for added wear and traction.

name: SRAM CenterLine Disc Brake Rotor
description: Keeping the center of friction consistent throughout rotation to minimize vibration, the SRAM CenterLine disc brake rotor provides a smooth, consistent and quiet-running braking surface. 180mm Diameter.

name: SRAM G2 R Hydraulic Disc Brake and Lever Set
description: A reliable brake solution that gives you plenty of power and precise control, this SRAM G2 R hydraulic disc brake and lever set is easy to install, maintain and adjust.

name: TRP Spyre Mechanical Disc Brake Caliper - Post Mount
description: Offering superior performance and easy setup, the post-mount TRP Spyre mechanical disc brake caliper uses a dual piston design to provide precise clamping force for even pad and rotor wear.

name: SRAM Level/DB/Elixir Disc Brake Pads
description: Original equipment pads for no-compromise disc brake performance, the SRAM Level/DB/Elixir disc brake pads feature a steel-backed organic compound for quieter braking.

name: SRAM Level T Hydraulic Disc Brake and Lever Set
description: A no-nonsense, trail-optimized brake solution with a compact lever body, this SRAM Level T hydraulic disc brake and lever set gives you plenty of reliable power and precise control.

name: NiteRider Lumina Micro 900 Front / Vmax+ 150 Rear Bike Light Set
description: A bright and compact combo, the NiteRider Lumina Micro 900 headlight and Vmax+ 150 USB-rechargeable taillight set work to help you see and be seen on rides in low-light conditions.

name: NiteRider Lumina Max 2000 Front Bike Light with NiteLink
description: A versatile, feature-rich, rechargeable headlight, the NiteRider Lumina Max 2000 features NiteLink™ wireless technology, enabling you to remotely control a compatible taillight (not included).

name: Knog Plug Front and Rear Bike Light Twinpack
description: Boasting unique domed lenses, the Knog Plug front and rear bike light twinpack provides you with 250 lumens up front and 10 lumens in the back to keep you visible while you explore the roads.

name: Bontrager Flare RT Rear Bike Light
description: Smaller and more powerful than its predecessor, the Bontrager Flare RT rear bike light helps you stay seen on every ride. Its distinctive flash, focus and range can be seen up to 2km away in daylight.

name: Cygolite Hypershot 350 Bike Taillight
description: Packing 350 lumens into its light, compact form, the powerful Cygolite Hypershot 350 bike taillight flashes in a wide and long-range beam pattern that makes your bike stand out both day and night.

name: Specialized S-WORKS Tarmac SL7 RTP Frameset
description: 52cm frame - An aerodynamic lightweight frame built to deliver a race bike that is truly without compromise, along with a perfect canvas for custom paints.

name: SE Racing Floval Flyer 24in BMX Cruiser Frame and Fork
description: The SE 24in Floval Flyer XL Frame is for the cruiser racer who wants a little extra room and stability. The geometry is perfect for the cruiser class, and with its bi-oval downtube it's the stiffest Floval Flyer ever produced. The Pro Cruiser has a 21.2in toptube while the Pro Cruiser XL is a bit longer with a 22in toptube.

name: Specialized 2022 Stumpjumper EVO Alloy Frameset
description: First things first, the Stumpjumper EVO Alloy isn't a normal trail bike. It's built to get gnarly, plain and simple. Featuring the same all-new design as its carbon brethren—including an adjustable head tube angle, 150mm of performance tuned travel, the adaptability of S-Sizing, and SWAT™ Door integration—in a lightweight yet tough M5 Alloy chassis, you're going to be able to bomb down trails that you thought you couldn't touch without a full-blown DH rig.

name: Continental Race Tube
description: Presta 42mm valve 700x18-25mm.

name: Continental Race Tube
description: Presta 60mm valve 700x18-25mm.

name: Slime brand Self-Sealing Bicycle Tube
description: Schrader 26in x 1.75-2.125in

name: Shimano EH500 SPD Sport Road Pedals
description: Clip in or flip the pedals over and crank on the wide platforms—you decide. The Shimano EH500 SPD Sport pedals work with cleats or without for multipurpose performance and ease.

name: Bontrager City Pedals
description: The Bontrager City Pedal set delivers comfortable support and reliable traction to keep you confidently connected to your bike during rides around town.

name: Shimano PD-ED500 Road Touring Pedals
description: Designed for lightweight road touring and commuter bikes, these SPD-compatible Shimano PD-ED500 pedals are perfect for those rides requiring frequent engagement and disengagement.

name: SRAM GX Eagle 12 Speed Bike Chain
description: Compatible with 12 speed drivetrains

name: Shimano HG71 6/7/8 Speed Bike Chain
description: Compatible with 6,7, or 8 speed drivetrains

name: Shimano Ultegra 10-speed Bike Chain
description: Compatible with 10 speed drivetrains

name: KMC X12 Silver Bike Chain
description: Compatible with 12 speed drivetrains
